name: Joy Madamba
text: [@paulakatarina](https://twitter.com/paulakatarina/) [@roytang](https://twitter.com/roytang/) Huh, onga. Ang naisip ko na lang na pwedeng gawin is automatically flag COD orders sa "hot" addresses (e.g. OVP, Sen Kiko's ofc, CHR, Sen Risa's ofc), and CSAs will call persons dun sa addresses to check na may COD order nga sila.
